fastlane/test_output

# Carthage (defensive)
Carthage/Build/

# Sparkle Distribution Phase 1 (2026-05-19) — local release DMG cache.
# DMGs live in GitHub Releases; the local releases/ folder is just the
# scratch space generate_appcast scans to produce appcast.xml. Never
# commit DMG binaries to git.
releases/

